                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7105" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IPR-0008</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7670 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中集大“吉”、胜狮难“胜”：“德国漏水器”专利 的中国故事</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CIMC defeats Singamas for the final victory: The chinese patent lawsuit story of the &quot;German Water Leakage&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙玉涛，王茜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海中集冷藏箱有限公司和上海胜狮冷冻货柜有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“漏水器专利”；独家许可；专利诉讼；抗辩；和解</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Water Leakage&quot; patent; exclusive license; litigation; defense; settlement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国集装箱行业领军企业中集向法院提起专利诉讼请求，指控竞争对手胜狮在未经自己同意的情况下私自使用“漏水器专利”，涉嫌侵犯自己的知识产权。从案例发生的背景来看，这场“漏水器专利”知识产权大战爆发于集装箱行业同质化竞争激烈，制造厂商纷纷向高端市场进军的关键时期。起初中集为了进入该市场，以独家许可的方式从德国瓦工堡公司获得了“漏水器专利”（冷藏箱核心技术之一），之后利用该技术生产并推出了自己的冷藏箱产品。然而新产品问世不久，中集发现市场上出现了由胜狮等厂商生产的、与之极其相似且成本更低的产品，认为这些厂商存在专利侵权的行为，遂决定就侵权问题与相关厂商进行协商沟通。在这一过程中，胜狮认为自己并未侵犯中集的专利权。沟通未果，中集决定通过诉讼方式保护自己的知识产权，而胜狮采取了一系列抗辩行为予以应对。
历时五年之久，2009年3月25日胜狮承认了自己的侵权行为，向中集致歉并赔偿经济损失。在法院调解下，集装箱两大巨头最终以和解的方式解决了此次专利纠纷。专利诉讼的胜利不仅使中集成功保护了自己的知识产权，弥补了部分经济损失，还在打击竞争对手的同时，提升了企业形象。实际上，在市场竞争日益激烈以及知识产权重要性愈发凸显的时代背景下，专利诉讼已成为企业维护自己的知识产权，构建市场进入壁垒的重要手段。对此，企业纷纷制定了专利诉讼战略来获得竞争优势，企业间的专利诉讼纠纷也日益频繁。通过对中集与胜狮的漏水器专利诉讼实际案例的回溯以及知识点的解读，本案例不仅可以帮助读者深刻掌握专利引进与运用和专利诉讼等专利战略核心知识内容，还可以从胜狮的具体回应学习到企业面临诉讼时可采取的抗辩方式以及和解策略相关内容。因此，本案例既能够强化企业管理者理论方面的学习，同时又可以为企业制定行之有效的专利攻防策略和专利战略提供实际的参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abstract: CIMC which is China&#39;s container industry leader filed a patent litigation request to the court, accusing rival Singamas of using the &quot;German Water Leakage&quot; patent without its agreement, allegedly infringing their intellectual property rights. The two manufacturers of this &quot;German Water Leakage&quot; patent intellectual property war broke out in the container industry homogeneous competition is fierce,so that manufacturers tried to enter the high-end market with characteristic of high technology content and large profit margin.The main character of the case CIMC in order to enter this market, firstly obtained the &quot;German Water Leakage&quot; patent (one of the core technology of reefer) by the way of exclusive license from the German Wagnerburg company,then used this technology to make and launch its own reefer products. However, soon afterwards, similar and lower-cost products produced by shegnshi and other manufacturers appeared in the market, which led to a serious negative impact on the competitiveness of CIMC&#39;s new products.CIMC believed that these manufacturers have patent infringement behavior, so it is decided to negotiate with related manufacturers on the infringement issue. In this process, Singamas thought that it has not infringed CIMC&#39;s patent rights. After unsuccessful negotiations with Singamas, CIMIC decided to protect its intellectual property rights through litigation. Singamas responded with a series of defensive actions.
On March 25, 2009,the day that aftet the suit was filed about five years, Singamas admitted its infringement, apologized to CIMC and compensated for financial losses. Under the mediation of the court, the two container giants finally settled the patent dispute by way of settlement. The victory of the patent litigation not only made CIMC successfully protect its intellectual property rights, compensate part of the economic loss, but also in the fight against competitors at the same time, enhance the corporate image. In fact, with the increasingly fierce competition in the market as well as the importance of intellectual property rights becoming more and more prominent,patent litigation has become an important means for enterprises to defend their intellectual property rights and build barriers to market. In response, enterprises have formulated patent litigation strategies to gain competitive advantages, and patent litigation disputes among enterprises have become increasingly frequent. Through the discussion and interpretation of the patent litigation case between CIMC and Singamas, readers not only profoundly grasp the core knowledge of patent strategy such as patent introduction and application and patent litigation, but also can learn from the specific ways of defending against the litigation from Singamas&#39;s response and enhance their knowledge of the importance of patent as a strategic resource. Therefore, this case is conducive to enhancing managers&#39; awareness of the importance of patents as a strategic resource, and has certain inspiration and reference value for enterprises to make patent strategies and the effective patent attack and defense strategies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2003</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《知识产权管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业专利引进与利用战略；发起诉讼的动机、收益；专利诉讼风险；被诉方的和解与积极抗辩策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
